&quot;there are sites and plug-ins that can manage your e-mail and make it reappear at the top of your in-box at a specified date. Services like Nudgemail, Followup, Followupthen and Boomerang allow you to schedule a message to reappear as new in your in-box later by allowing you to forward the message to yourself with a time delay — from an hour to weeks or months.&quot;

